Please be brief, counselor.

687
00:33:34,630 --> 00:33:36,160
好的
Yes, of course.

688
00:33:39,690 --> 00:33:40,820
她會來
She'll be here.

689
00:33:41,930 --> 00:33:43,560
你有想盤問他的嗎
Do you have anything for cross?

690
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:45,790
我能看一下你的筆記嗎
Can I look at your notes?

691
00:33:45,970 --> 00:33:47,490
當然可以
Yeah, of course.

692
00:33:47,530 --> 00:33:48,940
我們能...
Can we, um...

693
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:50,700
好的
Yeah.

694
00:34:02,610 --> 00:34:03,990
很高興你能來
So glad you made it.

695
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:09,420
