Everybody, please be back and ready to go on the hour.

700
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,960
-麗貝卡  -查克
- Rebecca. - Chuck.

701
00:34:32,680 --> 00:34:33,590
很高興見到你
It's good to see you.

702
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:36,610
不得不說  我有點兒意外
I have to say, I'm a bit surprised.

703
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:38,610
